# Web Scraping: Largest Automotive Suppliers

This project uses Python to scrape data from the Wikipedia page on the **List of the Largest Automotive Suppliers**.

 
[Wikipedia - List of the largest automotive suppliers](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_the_largest_automotive_suppliers)

